How to upload photos:

1. The location on the server is:
    - PRODUCTION site path is: '/var/www/tansycloud.com/public/photos'
    - DEV site path is: '/var/www/dev.tansycloud.com/public/photos'

2. The folder and file permissions:
    - the user and user group should be 'www-data:www-data' (The apache web server user)
    - the permissions should be 775

    Example commands to upload photos:

        cd /var/www/dev.tansycloud.com/public
        mkdir photos

        chown www-data:www-data photos
        chmod 775 photos

        chown www-data:www-data image.png
        chmod 775 image.png



